OL,3,CDenise Nolan pays tribute to late
OL,4,Csister Linda
OL,6,FDenise Nolan has been speaking about
OL,7,Fthe final days with her beloved sister
OL,8,FLinda before she passed away on 15
OL,9,FJanuary at the age of 65.
OL,11,FThe Irish singer rose to fame in
OL,12,Ffamily group The Nolans with sisters
OL,13,FColeen, Maureen, Bernie, Denise and
OL,14,FAnne. She died earlier this month,
OL,15,Fsurrounded by family, after being
OL,16,Fadmitted to hospital in Blackpool with
OL,17,Fdouble pneumonia.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
