OL,3,CDenise Nolan pays tribute to late
OL,4,Csister Linda
OL,6,FDenise said she travelled to the
OL,7,Fhospital in an ambulance with her
OL,8,Fsister, who had cancer, and added that
OL,9,Fher decline in health and death felt
OL,10,F"very sudden".
OL,12,FDenise said she is "doing as well as
OL,13,Fcan be expected but it will be hard at
OL,14,Fthe funeral. There are days when you
OL,15,Fdon't think about it and then all of a
OL,16,Fsudden it hits you, little things that
OL,17,Fcome up and you forget she's gone,
OL,18,Fit's really hard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
