OL,3,CDenise Nolan pays tribute to late
OL,4,Csister Linda
OL,6,FDenise added: "It was very sudden
OL,7,Freally and it wasn't the cancer that
OL,8,Fgot her in the end, she could have
OL,9,Flived another few years but she got
OL,10,Fpneumonia and her immune system was so
OL,11,Fbad she couldn't handle it, but I say
OL,12,Fto anyone with cancer you can still
OL,13,Fget on with it if you have Linda's
OL,14,Fattitude you can live with it for
OL,15,Fyears like she did."
OL,17,FShe also said some people were finding
OL,18,Fit hard to come to her house, where
OL,19,FLinda was staying, as they say
OL,20,F'There's too many memories of Linda
OL,21,Fthere. I can't handle it'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
