OL,3,CDenise Nolan pays tribute to late
OL,4,Csister Linda
OL,6,FDenise said she has been touched by
OL,7,Fthe tributes being paid to Linda: "I
OL,8,Fknew she had some amazing friends and
OL,9,Fthat's the sign of a great person when
OL,10,Fyou have lots of people who love you,
OL,11,Fbut I didn't know the outpouring of
OL,12,Fgrief from fans, they were so upset to
OL,13,Flose her and for a lot of people who
OL,14,Fhave had cancer she was their
OL,15,Finspiration."
OL,17,FLinda had been a long-time campaigner
OL,18,Fand fundraiser for cancer awareness,
OL,19,Fhaving been diagnosed with breast
OL,20,Fcancer in 2005.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
